name: Yamada Elf (Emily) | Eromanga-sensei
description:
LoRA is generated entirely from anime images.
Should work well with any model. NSFW works nicely too.

Check samples for prompts :)
For anime clothes just be specific in describing them.
However some of her clothes can be harder to generate,
but give it a few re-runs and you should get a positive result.

Leave a like, comment, review but first of all, ENJOY ;)
